=== RESONANCE_CRYSTAL ===
# id: 11
# title: The Resonance Crystal
# chinese_title: 共鸣石
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A crystal formation has grown through a breach in the hull, fed by cosmic radiation. It hums at a frequency you can feel in your bones. The crystal's facets contain tiny inclusions that look like frozen lightning.

* [Harvest a section of the crystal]
  ~ gain_radical("雷")
  "雷" (léi) — thunder, lightning
* [Record the resonance frequency]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "音" (yīn) — sound, tone
* [Touch the crystal to feel its vibration]
  ~ heal(10)
  "感" (gǎn) — to feel, sensation
